            "postType": "article",
            "summary": "The US economy added 175,000 jobs in February, beating expectations. The unemployment rate rose to 6.7%. Here\u2019s the breakdown of employment status for all Americans age 16 and above: Here\u2019s what job creation and loss looked like in various industries last month:",
